name: setBeautyEffectOptions
description:
Sets the image enhancement options.Since
  v3.0.0 (Windows), v3.2.0 (macOS)
       
   
   Enables or disables image enhancement and sets the options.
   Call this method after enableVideo.

parameters.enabled:
Whether to enable the image enhancement function:
      true: Enable the image enhancement function.
      false: (Default) Disable the image enhancement function.

parameters.options: The image enhancement options. See BeautyOptions.
